timing_enable_...ound_constants(25.10)  timing_enable_...ound_constants(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_power_ground_constants

Syntax
       timing_enable_power_ground_constants

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Determines if case analysis is inferred from power and ground rail con-
       nections/nets, e.g., VDD and GND.

       When  set to true, the software recognizes the constants that come from
       power and ground rail connections.

       When set to false, the software ignores these constants. This  provides
       the most intuitive behavior with logical style netlist (and other tools
       that do not read physical data).

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

